{"data":{"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"EUCARDIA: Cardiovascular risk prediction for the Greek population using AI models","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/abaa8/EUKARDIA_LOGO.png","srcSet":"/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/e8baf/EUKARDIA_LOGO.png 133w,\n/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/12aa5/EUKARDIA_LOGO.png 266w,\n/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/abaa8/EUKARDIA_LOGO.png 531w","sizes":"(min-width: 531px) 531px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/3cfe7/EUKARDIA_LOGO.avif 133w,\n/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/4e1fe/EUKARDIA_LOGO.avif 266w,\n/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/052a9/EUKARDIA_LOGO.avif 531w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 531px) 531px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/08e42/EUKARDIA_LOGO.webp 133w,\n/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/38ac8/EUKARDIA_LOGO.webp 266w,\n/static/75cedcef26ca1dd9cbcb1ab429cd2865/41cc2/EUKARDIA_LOGO.webp 531w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 531px) 531px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":452.16572504708097}}},"tech":["Python","ScikitLearn"],"github":null,"external":null},"html":"<p>As a subcontractor of <a href=\"https://www.raymed.gr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">RAYMED</a> I developed the EUCARDIA model in the context of a research project funded by the Greek Secretary of Research and Inovation.\nEUCARDIA is the first AI-based model for accurate 10-year risk prediction for cardiovascular disease for the Greek population.\nMore on <a href=\"https://eukardia.gr/en/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">EUCARDIA website</a></p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Short-term precipitation forecasting using Convolutional LSTM neural networks","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/36d39/lstm.png","srcSet":"/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/8dd46/lstm.png 175w,\n/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/33140/lstm.png 350w,\n/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/36d39/lstm.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/62f37/lstm.avif 175w,\n/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/5bf13/lstm.avif 350w,\n/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/26659/lstm.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/d7dea/lstm.webp 175w,\n/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/9044e/lstm.webp 350w,\n/static/d5413b2f56fb86f004347e812d1cdf4f/b5196/lstm.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":264}}},"tech":["Python","Tensorflow","Keras"],"github":"https://github.com/petrosDemetrakopoulos/LSTM-radar-precipitation-forecast","external":null},"html":"<p>An autoencoder implemented using a Convolutional LSTM Neural Network that forecasts precipitation (in the short term) from real weather radar data.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Face mask detection with neural networks","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/b3a47/face.jpg","srcSet":"/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/3ea88/face.jpg 175w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/230e3/face.jpg 350w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/b3a47/face.jpg 700w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/7ddc1/face.jpg 1400w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/19d98/face.avif 175w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/b52d4/face.avif 350w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/b093c/face.avif 700w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/5166d/face.avif 1400w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/eac4f/face.webp 175w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/3eafe/face.webp 350w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/4ff0e/face.webp 700w,\n/static/11ac86781a96a1e7dd0212f6f374b3aa/6e235/face.webp 1400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":353}}},"tech":["Python","Keras"],"github":"https://github.com/petrosDemetrakopoulos/face-mask-detector","external":null},"html":"<p>This project demonstrates how a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) can detect if a person in a picture is wearing a face mask or not. As you can easily understand the applications of this method may be very helpful for the prevention and the control of COVID-19 as it could be used in public places like airports, shopping malls etc.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Ethair Balloons","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/ed88c/ethairballoons1.png","srcSet":"/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/4e016/ethairballoons1.png 175w,\n/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/e3c36/ethairballoons1.png 350w,\n/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/ed88c/ethairballoons1.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/5a56e/ethairballoons1.avif 175w,\n/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/a1848/ethairballoons1.avif 350w,\n/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/869b9/ethairballoons1.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/865bb/ethairballoons1.webp 175w,\n/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/3cb5e/ethairballoons1.webp 350w,\n/static/022763baefa9e1904d6eda3c09703401/a470f/ethairballoons1.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":219}}},"tech":["Solidity","Javascript"],"github":"https://github.com/petrosDemetrakopoulos/ethairballoons","external":"https://www.npmjs.com/package/ethairballoons"},"html":"<p>A strictly typed ORM library for Ethereum blockchain. It allows developers to use Ethereum blockchain as a persistent storage in an organized and model-oriented way without writing custom complex Smart contracts. The library is available for installation <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/ethairballoons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">via npm</a></p>"}}]}}}